      • matches

        public boolean matches(Object actual)
        从接口复制的说明: ArgumentMatcher
        Informs if this matcher accepts the given argument.

        The method should never assert if the argument doesn't match. It should only return false.

        See the example in the top level javadoc for ArgumentMatcher

        指定者:
        matches 在接口中 ArgumentMatcher<Object>
        参数:
        actual - the argument
        返回:
        true if this matcher accepts the given argument.

        public boolean typeMatches(Object target)
        从接口复制的说明: ContainsExtraTypeInfo
        Checks if target target has matching type. If the type matches, there is no point in rendering result from ContainsExtraTypeInfo.toStringWithType()
